[Misc.\P1 Move Modifier (All Fighters + Unplayable Fighters)]
author=Hacc
description=How to work it for Arcade, Time Attack, VS, and Team Battle modes:

1) Select the character whose moves you 
want to use (normal fighter). 
To use the unplayable fighters moves (excluding Metal Mokujin), 
hold R3 and choose any character.
2) Immediately after selecting your character, 
hold L1+Select (normal fighter) or R3 (unplayable fighter) 
until you see their intro.
3) After "Fight" is announced, press L3 to kill yourself.
4) Once at the character select screen again, 
select the fighter you want to use the moves with.
5) Immediately after selecting your character,
hold L1+Select (normal fighter) or R3 (unplayable fighter) 
until you see their intro. You will now be using the previous 
character's moves. 
If you lose a match and still want to use those same moves 
for another character; hold L1+Select (normal fighter) or R3
(unplayable fighter) after selecting your new character. 
To set new moves for your character, do the following:

1) Pick a new character and don't hold any buttons.
2) Once "Fight" is announced, press L3 to kill yourself.
3) Repeat steps 1-5 above.


Swapping normal character moves between each other 
(excluding story mode):

How to work it it for Practice mode:

1) Select the character whose moves you want to use 
(normal fighter). To use the special fighters moves
(excluding Metal Mokujin), hold R3 and choose any character. 
Choose anybody as the CPU.
2) Immediately after selecting the stage to fight on, 
hold L1+Select (normal fighter) or R3 (unplayable fighter) 
until the match starts.
3) Pause and return to the character select screen.
4) At the character select screen, select the fighter you want 
to use the moves with.
5) Immediately after selecting the stage to fight on, 
hold L1+Select (normal fighter) or R3 (unplayable fighter) 
until the match starts. 
You will now be using the previous character's moves. 
To set new moves for your character, do the following:

1) Pick a new character and don't hold any buttons.
2) Once the match starts, pause and return to character select screen.
3) Repeat steps 1-5 above.

1) Pick the fighter whose moves you want to use for another fighter. 
After selcecting, immediately hold L1+Select until the match starts.

2) When the match starts, press L3 to kill yourself. 
Press Start to return to the character select screen.

3) Choose the player you want to use the moves with and 
immediately hold L1+Select until the match starts. 
The fighter should now be using the previous fighters moves. 
Note: If you win the match and want to continue using the moves, 
hold L1+Select during their winning pose until the next match starts. 
Lose? just choose a different fighter and hold L1+Select 
until the match starts. They will now be using the moves.

4B - Jinpachi (Demon 1)
4C - Jinpachi (Demon 2)
4D - Jinpachi (Human 1)
4E - Jinpachi (Human 2)
4F - Metal Mokujin
